{
  "stem": "512.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have to march, and they'll kill me if I show up without it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What am I going to do?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I had a cousin that worked in the warehouse, so she jeopardized her life-- she wasn't supposed to-- and ran early in the morning and asked one of the Nazis to open it up, because she said she forgot something there and she needed it badly.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So she stole a, a pair of wooden clogs and brought it for me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Otherwise they would have killed me there without having them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Once, once it was bitter cold, so I took a little piece of a blanket, and I tied it around me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Skinny, I was terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I tied it around because I was bitter cold.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then a Nazi pulled me out, and she spotted on me the blanket.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She beat the daylight out of me, because I-- government property I, I had taken out from the barrack.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So I knew for the next time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But life was going pretty smoothly until they stopped manufacturing the bombs.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then it was already closer to spring.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "No, it was still winter, yeah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Then they started-- they took us, and they started digging ditches.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that's where I-- my hands were frozen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My legs and my toes got frozen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I suffered after liberation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "After the thing I suffered a lot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Every year it would get terribly infected.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it was something that I didn't want to go to a doctor, and I didn't want to talk about it, even then.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Things like that, that I refused to go see a doctor, but I suffered.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "My hands were-- ran with pus and all that, very infected.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Still have marks.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
